### ============================================
### OUTDAR Auth Tests
### Click "Send Request" above each block to test
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api

### ----------------------------------------------
### TEST 1: Health check (sanity)
### Expected: 200 OK with success message
### ----------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ----------------------------------------------
### TEST 2: Register a new user (YOU!)
### Expected: 201 Created with user + token
### ----------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jaafar B.",
  "email": "jaafar@outdar.test",
  "password": "test1234",
  "city": "Casablanca",
  "role": "host"
}

### ----------------------------------------------
### TEST 3: Try registering same email AGAIN
### Expected: 400 — "already exists"
### ----------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jaafar B.",
  "email": "jaafar@outdar.test",
  "password": "test1234",
  "city": "Casablanca"
}

### ----------------------------------------------
### TEST 4: Login with correct credentials
### Expected: 200 with user + token
### IMPORTANT: Copy the token from the response,
### you'll need it for TEST 6
### ----------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jaafar@outdar.test",
  "password": "test1234"
}

### ----------------------------------------------
### TEST 5: Login with WRONG password
### Expected: 401 — "Invalid email or password"
### ----------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jaafar@outdar.test",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### ----------------------------------------------
### TEST 6: Get current user (PROTECTED ROUTE!)
### Expected: 200 with your user data
### IMPORTANT: Replace YOUR_TOKEN_HERE with the
### token you got from TEST 4 (login)
### ----------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiI2OWY0MGEzOWI5NDlkYzllOGJjYjQ3NTQiLCJyb2xlIjoiaG9zdCIsImlhdCI6MTc3NzYwMzA0OSwiZXhwIjoxNzc4MjA3ODQ5fQ.Urntm-w_jTGOubOXK9IvaOlV-COKn42yvFA1j-HFS0A

### ----------------------------------------------
### TEST 7: Get current user WITHOUT token
### Expected: 401 — "Not authenticated"
### ----------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me